properties.DESCRIPTION:
Saya status is india's tallest mall located in sector 129, right on noida expressway. It is a remarkable feat of modern architecture and engineering developed by saya group. The project spans approx. 1.4 million sq. Ft and consists of 9 floors of stunning vertical development. The development boasts of innovative design and architectural values, offering a range of luxury amenities. It is expected to set new benchmarks in the retail industry and provide a fresh experience to customers. 
The construction of the project is in full swing, with the mall set to open its doors to visitors in january 2025. It has been designed by the globally renowned architectural firm dp architects, based in singapore. Its launch gathered enthusiastic response, and we have already signed with several popular retail brands including: Tim hortons, aldo, charles & keith, victoria's secret, inglot, bath & body works, tim hortons, haldiram's, forever new, punjab grill, youmee, diaso japan, r&b and many more. 
 
From high-End fashion to electronic gadgets, the mall offers something for everyone. Its stunning faade and interior design are complemented by exceptional utilities like a multi-Level car parking facility. With space for over 1600 cars, it is one of the largest parking spaces in the area. Visitors can also access the mall through various modes of transport, including the metro and other public transport options. 
 
A meticulous zoning plan makes every floor of saya status a destination in itself. 
The lower ground floor- Superstores (Food, grocery & electronics stores) 
Ground floor- International and premium fashion stores 
First floor- Men's fashion (Formal wear, sportswear, footwear & bags) 
Second floor- Women's fashion (Apparel, accessories and cosmetics) and home dcor 
Third floor- Expansive food and fun zone (Food court, family zone, entertainment center & toys) 
Fourth floor- Multiplex (6 screens and a seating capacity of 1300 pax) and fine-Dining restaurants 
Fifth floor- Gold and jewellery 
Sixth floor- Wedding collections & indian designer wear 
Seventh floor- Wellness hub (Wellness clinics, cosmetic clinics and gyms) 
Eight floor & ninth floor- Premium clubs, pubs & bars 
 
It also hosts a play area for children, making it an ideal destination for families. 
 
Saya status is set to become the region's retail epicenter, attracting visitors from all over the city and beyond. Its state-Of-The-Art facilities and luxurious shopping experience make it a must-Visit destination for anyone looking for a day out. Saya status is a testament to saya group's commitment to providing world-Class infrastructure and amenities. Its unique design, vast shopping options, and luxury amenities make it a path-Breaking retail structure unlike what the region is used to.
